\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces  Synthetic validation dataset: estimator recovery of the known treatment effect ($\tau = 2.0$, dashed line). Regression adjustment, IPW, and doubly robust estimation are all within 3.7\% of truth. The dashed reference line marks the data-generating effect, making the downward bias of nearest-neighbor matching visually apparent relative to the other estimators.}}{9}{figure.4}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:synthetic}{{4}{9}{Synthetic validation dataset: estimator recovery of the known treatment effect ($\tau = 2.0$, dashed line). Regression adjustment, IPW, and doubly robust estimation are all within 3.7\% of truth. The dashed reference line marks the data-generating effect, making the downward bias of nearest-neighbor matching visually apparent relative to the other estimators}{figure.4}{}}
